eu.amidst.core.variables

Interface Variable


  • public interface Variable
    This interface handles a Variable of a Bayesian network. The Variable contains information such as observable or not, the state space type and the distribution type.

    For an example of use follow this link

    http://amidst.github.io/toolbox/CodeExamples.html#bnexample
